496
00:41:23,820 --> 00:41:26,050
- Ayolah!
- Putar! Putar!

497
00:41:26,189 --> 00:41:27,486
Hentikan!

498
00:41:27,557 --> 00:41:29,149
- Gunakan sesuatu.
- Hentikan.

499
00:41:29,225 --> 00:41:30,214
Sesuatu apa!

