00:41:33,463 --> 00:41:35,363
Ada jendela di sini.

501
00:41:36,766 --> 00:41:38,859
- Penangkalnya ada padanya.
- Hentikan!

502
00:41:38,935 --> 00:41:40,334
Ambil dia kalau begitu.

503
00:41:42,639 --> 00:41:44,038
- Cepat!
- Terbukalah.

504
00:41:44,207 --> 00:41:46,869
- Sial!
